e":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c551023440f6c286435d719d162fa044da076253","tid":934503,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"你地日屌夜屌搞到人地要告人拎返啲面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港田徑代表隊「欄后」呂麗瑤去年報稱被前中學教練性侵，事後她一度遭網友質疑為何不報警，甚至對她作出種種攻擊。《南華早報》報道，呂麗瑤今日表示，正考慮對一連串攻擊她的網上言論採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，呂麗瑤今日獲香港業餘田徑總會頒予53,000元，表揚她雅加達亞運中的表演。她在受訪時談及性侵事件，形容自己情緒已經恢復過來，「但仍有一些人繼續通過互聯網攻擊我」。<br />\n<br />\n她指難以解釋這些網民的行為，「也許除了這種毫無意義的行為，他們無所事事。有些人甚至使用虛假的帳戶，聲稱要促進香港體育運動發局，向我索取資金。」她表示正與經理人商討，「法律行動是其中一個選項」。<br />\n<br />\n呂麗瑤在去年11月30日凌晨在FB撰文，公開自已十四、五歲時被前任教練性侵的經歷，並指自己的剖白是為了喚起公眾對兒童性侵犯的關注。此一事件迅速成為全港焦點，在一開始體壇、官員、議員等一面倒表態支持呂麗瑤的勇敢行為後，網絡上亦出現不少言論，質疑呂麗瑤為何十年後才說出經歷，又批評她婉拒報警的做法，認為是對被指控者不公。<br />\n<br />\n而在今年11月，一名曾任田徑教練的77歲退休人士黃恆，涉於8年前在大埔住所藉詞替女學員按摩，強扯對方內褲非禮，案件經審訊後裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%8D%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%2591%2582%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2591%25A4%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%258E%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F&d=8S8G0peBvkyZaqVbO4V6CjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0101a9b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%2591%2582%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2591%25A4%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%258E%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F&h=c70e0bf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1-%E5%91%82%E9%BA%97%E7%91%A4%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%8D%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"真心笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地教練俾你屈完都未告番你<br />\n先告左路人 繼續燒起把火<br />\n提高自己關注度？"},{"pid":"27d6472400b5bf49f1fdc0011691f195756128de","tid":934503,"uid":79557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"#youtoo"},{"pid":"03192d95e0ad3a72c569b9eb4ae83fd9024304c7","tid":934503,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"告得幾多個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e5767263086bad39c98d6e400422dca69a4a10","tid":934503,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03192d95e0ad3a72c569b9eb4ae83fd9024304c7","tid":934503,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"告得幾多個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"民事要起到底先俾到告票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389d1498c78929a58e6be8600efdfb7b44bdafde","tid":934503,"uid":53238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:12:06.000Z","msg":"屈唔到人發脾 4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458b5bb25ce17c98c5615cf60d33ed12ccb301c3","tid":934503,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28e5767263086bad39c98d6e400422dca69a4a10","tid":934503,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03192d95e0ad3a72c569b9eb4ae83fd9024304c7","t